{"tid":2189463,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"不丹（唔只係梁朝偉劉嘉玲結婚嘅地方）","createTime":"2020-09-05T02:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T17:20:42.000Z","uid":323949,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cee09988b7b95ad1b9a2e3e2bd70648dde5ce711","tid":2189463,"uid":323949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"講起不丹，大部分人都只知道係梁朝偉劉嘉玲結婚嘅地方（遲d會講去佢地結婚間酒店食Tea），不過，不丹有更多值得大家探索嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n去不丹一定要跟團先可以申請簽證。因為不丹旅遊收費有分淡旺季，我係2018年6月頭（雨季開始前同埋淡季頭）去，每人每晚最低消費200美元，包3星酒店、食宿同門票，機票另計。我無經香港旅行社，而係直接同Tripadvisor上面第一名嘅當地旅行社訂，所以簽證經email寄畀我。我嘅4日3夜行程：<br />\nParo&gt;Thimphu&gt;Punakha&gt;Ha&gt;Paro <br />\n(我無行上Paro Taktsang而去了Ha，當日遇到寺廟開幕，畀我見到基堪布（職位僅次於不丹國王），同埋我路上都有係遠處見到不丹國王)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTCSRoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTCSRoO.jpg&h=4dd1431c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tU8iMXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtU8iMXg.jpg&h=f384227f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於CX Fanfare當時有特價去Kathmandu，所以我由Kathmandu飛去不丹嘅Paro，而飛行途中可以見到珠峰（係曼￿飛無得睇）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mkw4HvU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkw4HvU.jpg&h=91b406c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按不丹旅遊規定，就算你一個人去都會包團，所以一到步就見到我地嘅私人導遊同司機。導遊係一位媽媽，過幾日我地在旅途上都有見到佢個女，而導遊同司機嘅英文同服務都好好。<br />\n<br />\n不丹係農業社會，所以路上可以見到好多農田：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aeTOpKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaeTOpKs.jpg&h=a52cb1a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為藏傳佛教國家，不丹大部分景點都同宗教有關，例如Dzong，一個畀僧人同政府用嘅城堡建築:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7mkfRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7mkfRv.jpg&h=3e79e263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sq05rYc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsq05rYc.jpg&h=9bef53cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjb8pKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsjb8pKY.jpg&h=413b365f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6b3691a18db31afb750c28647027aac615b3f80","tid":2189463,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:21:27.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9a526d7448851400fce40a8b836cd36ac30d4c2f","tid":2189463,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2c39a219b4127a1f927e884f230d92384611e57f","tid":2189463,"uid":35682,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"第一句唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518642bc6b825747ed7c1ae1edd6c577978119f9","tid":2189463,"uid":240630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:37:18.000Z","msg":"不丹都好想去<br />\nLM 等update"},{"pid":"82fb24010da9de7f69ae8c6095aea375164df37d","tid":2189463,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"479ac16f110f94b79fe7f851933f025d70482eea","tid":2189463,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:43:53.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"38f93019b4258ce38473e519a9b566c84e76ce5e","tid":2189463,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee09988b7b95ad1b9a2e3e2bd70648dde5ce711","tid":2189463,"uid":323949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"講起不丹，大部分人都只知道係梁朝偉劉嘉玲結婚嘅地方（遲d會講去佢地結婚間酒店食Tea），不過，不丹有更多值得大家探索嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n去不丹一定要跟團先可以申請簽證。因為不丹旅遊收費有分淡旺季，我係2018年6月頭（雨季開始前同埋淡季頭）去，每人每晚最低消費200美元，包3星酒店、食宿同門票，機票另計。我無經香港旅行社，而係直接同Tripadvisor上面第一名嘅當地旅行社訂，所以簽證經email寄畀我。我嘅4日3夜行程：<br />\nParo&gt;Thimphu&gt;Punakha&gt;Ha&gt;Paro <br />\n(我無行上Paro Taktsang而去了Ha，當日遇到寺廟開幕，畀我見到基堪布（職位僅次於不丹國王），同埋我路上都有係遠處見到不丹國王)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTCSRoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F